prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D cartoon illustration for a greeting card front. A dreamy fantasy scene with a humorous twist. In a magical, enchanted forest clearing under a twilight sky filled with soft pastel clouds and shimmering stars, Lao Lao (person on the left in the photo) is depicted as a powerful fantasy queen. She sits majestically on an ornate, glowing mushroom throne, holding a ridiculously oversized, steaming boba tea like a royal scepter. She has a happy, slightly smug expression, wearing an elegant gown that creatively incorporates the style of her blue sweatshirt from the photo. Floating around her are glowing, mischievous fairies. Jordan (person on the right in the photo) is depicted as her comically devoted knight, wearing armor that mimics his brown hoodie from the photo. He kneels beside the throne, presenting Lao Lao with a giant, beautifully wrapped birthday cake that is teetering precariously. He has a slightly panicked but adoring expression. The entire scene is filled with magical, ethereal elements like sparkling fireflies, glowing flora, and a soft, magical haze.

In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a shimmering gold color, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my Queen, Lao Lao".
